text: State Superintendent of Education is an elected office of a constitutional nature in some U.S. states and may refer to: *California State Superintendent of Public Instruction *North Carolina Superintendent of Public Instruction *Oklahoma Superintendent of Public Instruction *Oregon Superintendent of Public Instruction *Texas Commissioner of Education *Washington State Superintendent of Public Instruction *Wisconsin Superintendent of Public Instruction Category:State superintendents of public instruction of the United States
title: State Superintendent of Public Instruction
